    pieces of Ulteo OVD are supported on openSUSE 11.2 system.
  </para>

  <section id="prerequisites">
    <title>Prerequisites: openSUSE 11.2</title>

    <para>
      openSUSE 11.2 was the latest stable version until August
      2010. It can be
      downloaded <ulink url="http://software.opensuse.org">here</ulink>.
    </para>

